column16: Charlie Culberson pops out to second baseman Carlos Asuaje.
Howie Kendrick flies out to center fielder Manuel Margot.
Andre Ethier singles on a ground ball to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.   Andrew Toles scores.
Joc Pederson strikes out on a foul tip.
Rob Segedin doubles (2) on a line drive to center fielder Manuel Margot.
Cristhian Adames grounds out, second baseman Alexi Amarista to first baseman Brett Wallace.
Charlie Blackmon singles on a ground ball to center fielder Travis Jankowski.
Jon Gray strikes out on a foul tip.
Kelby Tomlinson lines into a double play, second baseman Ryan Schimpf to shortstop Luis Sardinas.   Ehire Adrianza doubled off 2nd.
Angel Pagan lines out to left fielder Alex Dickerson.
Conor Gillaspie walks.   Ehire Adrianza to 2nd.
Chris Young flies out to center fielder Travis Jankowski.
Jackie Bradley Jr.   grounds into a double play, first baseman Wil Myers to shortstop Adam Rosales to first baseman Wil Myers.   Sandy Leon out at 2nd.
Sandy Leon singles on a line drive to center fielder Travis Jankowski.
Hanley Ramirez homers (21) on a line drive to left field.
